attachments.title: How connected cars are turning into revenue-generating machines
attachments.text: History repeats herself, but she mumbles. Most of the time we can only in retrospect discern what she was trying to say. Sometimes, though, history&rsquo;s intent is clear. That's where we stand with the state of connected cars: History is repeating itself. There is a correspondence in the patterns of disruption when you compare the future of connected cars to the past of the smartphone industry.
